title: Element Make It Count - Italy 2015
description:
Congrats to NICO BROMO who won the MAKE IT COUNT contest in Brescia, Italy!
Nico won a spot in the European Finals that will take place in Bolzano, and a chance to win a trip to California to compete for Element sponsorship at Nyjah's park!

RESULTS : 

1
